headline: OPEN PLATFORM VIDEO TECHNOLOGY SUPPORTS SENIOR LIVING COMMUNITY'S OPEN VALUES
summary: Garden Spot Communities, a continuing care retirement facility in New Holland, Pennsylvania, has grown a comprehensive video security solution over nearly 20 years that maintains the facility's welcoming, open-door philosophy while ensuring resident safety. The community operates public restaurants and welcomes neighbors across its 230-acre campus while securing 1,100 residents using Milestone Systems XProtect video management software (VMS).

headline: Is Tencent a Bargain After Being Shortlisted for Starbucks China Stake in 2025?
summary: If you have been watching Tencent Holdings closely, you are not alone. Investors all over the world are debating whether there is more upside left after the stock's riveting streak. Over the past week alone, Tencent is up 5.8%, and the returns stretch even further: up 12.9% over the past month, a striking 52.3% year to date, and an eye-grabbing 72.6% in the last twelve months. While the five-year picture is more tempered at 32.7%, few companies can match Tencent's impressive 128.1% return...

summary: The S&P 500 (^GSPC) is home to the biggest and most well-known companies in the market, making it a go-to index for investors seeking stability. But not all large-cap stocks are created equal - some are struggling with slowing growth, declining margins, or increased competition.

headline: 3 Reasons to Sell SBUX and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
